User - Anyone is who use the app ( Anyone is allowed).

Username - The identity of topics or comments. Reqiured each time at the beggining of the programe.

Topics - Listed in the main page. Each topics may contain pictures. And users comments in topics. (Also can be regarded as TOP-Level Comments)

Comments - Comments are added in topics. Comments can reply to comments.

Picture - Bitmap Picture which can be optional include in comment or topic.

Location - The location that located by User's device.

Edit Comment - User are allowed to edit their own comments (Identified by UserName).

Last topic - The topic that added the latest. Would be shown on the top sepcial part.

Greatest topic - The most popular topic that has the largest number of comments. Also will be shown on the top sepcial part.
